# Local Development - Backend Setup

Create `backend/.env` with these values for local development:

MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://your-user:your-password@cluster.mongodb.net/foodbank
JWT_SECRET=SmartFoodBank2024_SuperSecretKey
AI_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5001
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=8080

# Optional Cloudinary (if you want file uploads locally)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your_api_key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your_api_secret

# Then run:
# cd backend && npm start
# cd ai-services && python app.py  (in another terminal)
# cd frontend && npm run dev        (in another terminal)
